    "name": "Bloom - a puzzle adventure",
    "steam_appid": 3300090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/035d16a12824d8b8fee0f22066336768.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/035d16a12824d8b8fee0f22066336768.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bloom - 解谜冒险》是一款关于连锁反应和一只疯狂喜欢浆果的小狗的方块解谜游戏。和Arya以及她的小狗Bo一起，在充满活力的场景与可爱的故事中，结识风趣角色，挑战数百个令人烧脑的方块谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拯救世界完成了吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅玩由玩家们创作的无尽关卡，或用超简单的关卡编辑器制作自己的谜题，与朋友分享！展现你的创意，成为世界上最棒的关卡创作者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/c9446c5eb62add9d754afbf68dc0d358.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/c9446c5eb62add9d754afbf68dc0d358.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/c9446c5eb62add9d754afbf68dc0d358.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/2493cb53a4d89a30fcf979d63262af3b.avif?t=1768081500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras_big/2493cb53a4d89a30fcf979d63262af3b.avif?t=1768081500 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a842861cc198acdb596f7fd34fb30689.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a842861cc198acdb596f7fd34fb30689.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a842861cc198acdb596f7fd34fb30689.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单手操作，轻松上手，玩法简单但充满挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/5ef67756ee33fce3a688ae14c8acf716.avif?t=1768081500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras_big/5ef67756ee33fce3a688ae14c8acf716.avif?t=1768081500 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/61c3ecfccf8554536daf4b69029f2110.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/61c3ecfccf8554536daf4b69029f2110.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/61c3ecfccf8554536daf4b69029f2110.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受数百个拥有新机制和不断变化挑战的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a66710a7d56e6d98ee0daff91ac45152.avif?t=1768081500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras_big/a66710a7d56e6d98ee0daff91ac45152.avif?t=1768081500 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a4ddf7b9375ca2121a8fa218b3c70e29.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a4ddf7b9375ca2121a8fa218b3c70e29.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/a4ddf7b9375ca2121a8fa218b3c70e29.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随精彩故事，穿越12个独特场景，从郁郁葱葱的森林、外星星球到废弃的垃圾场和热闹的派对岛屿，结识可爱迷人的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/ed6fb193e5ac6e428f264b6f9639a39c.avif?t=1768081500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras_big/ed6fb193e5ac6e428f264b6f9639a39c.avif?t=1768081500 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9c283fb7443f6d620dfe437cb47f1c72.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9c283fb7443f6d620dfe437cb47f1c72.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9c283fb7443f6d620dfe437cb47f1c72.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用简单的拖拽编辑器制作你自己的谜题，与朋友分享。参与挑战，争夺每周排行榜最佳创作者的称号！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/0678d4c460ed072c6a500f3ad8022e30.avif?t=1768081500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras_big/0678d4c460ed072c6a500f3ad8022e30.avif?t=1768081500 width=800 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/34945d821567f22d7e51deb598d1f136.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/34945d821567f22d7e51deb598d1f136.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/34945d821567f22d7e51deb598d1f136.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需额外购买，就能畅玩其他玩家创作的大量关卡。即使通关主线后，你依然有源源不断的新内容可体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9a3c0f7e6d9453375236a5c28e72694d.poster.avif?t=1768081500\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9a3c0f7e6d9453375236a5c28e72694d.webm?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300090/extras/9a3c0f7e6d9453375236a5c28e72694d.mp4?t=1768081500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
